Enriched with intense color, this lip color is designed to satisfy every beauty conscious womans desires. This amazing lip color is available in the shade of Cassis Passion - 375 which makes your lips look simply irresistible. Apart from protecting your lips from dryness, this lip color provides them with lasting hydration and intense color. The texture of this Loreal Paris Color Riche (Cassis Passion - 376) is creamy which easily glides onto your lips for a neat and perfect finish. Directions for Use Apply this lip color by starting from the centre. Gently work towards the outer edges of your lip for even coverage.
